  "1696220": {
    "name": "胡修狐",
    "steam_appid": 1696220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/07ff19044429274051f76ec8cfd68e91.poster.avif?t=1759909615\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/07ff19044429274051f76ec8cfd68e91.webm?t=1759909615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/07ff19044429274051f76ec8cfd68e91.mp4?t=1759909615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《胡修狐》是一款健康的科幻冒险游戏。玩家将扮演倒霉的太空机械师薇克丝，她坠落在一个禁止使用工具的神秘星球上。在她值得信赖的工具箱“小锡”的陪伴下，薇克丝穿越焦糖星，发现海盗留下的藏宝处，修理友好的家用电器，以及品尝当地的美味佳肴。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/628fbd1ea255356a833bd76d6d03b516.webp?t=1759909615\" width=446 height=40 /></span><br>你可以驾驶轻快的滑板飞车穿越地球，也可以使用重型动力装载机清理道路，还可以徒步踏上宁静的旅程，探索焦糖星的所有地标。一边哼着动听的音乐，一边探索秘密地点，在奇思妙想的谜题中考验自己的智力，最后在温暖的篝火旁，仰望星空，安然入睡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/dfc84391d9cf4e48b59c6230a1b2971a.avif?t=1759909615\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/5816034528552ee3e4ddb6524608414c.webp?t=1759909615\" width=446 height=26 /></span><br>使用硬币、绷带、发光香蕉……等非常规工具，修理个性张扬的机器，如热情洋溢的割草机。实现太空机械师的梦想，建造并操作巨型机甲，帮助当地机器人解决他们的奇特问题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/0bd0ce82241a732125b498cb19dd9355.avif?t=1759909615\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/327dbee3a9d85072f339f2d9c681b48f.webp?t=1759909615\" width=446 height=26 /></span><br>修理东西可能很辛苦，但以温馨的食物结束一天的工作总能让人心情舒畅。享受星球居民提供的美味佳肴，如家常汤、热腾腾的饭碗和完全没有过期的布丁。与热情好客的机器人共进晚餐，结交朋友，也许就能发现解决下一个任务的重要线索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/a25d2def05e91209ff4e92b7b62711cb.avif?t=1759909615\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/64b7993ef9907ed7fabf10e8a73ae4e5.webp?t=1759909615\" width=446 height=26 /></span><br>从一次不起眼的信标维修工作开始，薇克丝很快发现自己卷入的情况远不止她自己的故事。一名被疏远的兄弟在寻找他失散多年的手足，专业的人工智能在克服过去的创伤，以及两个星球派系之间持续不断的争斗，这些都是需要拆解和修复的纠缠不清的谜团中的一小部分。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/1d3950fe329ab701fcccb9e9755c7130.avif?t=1759909615\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/a396ef4bcccfcdade820a5efcd6f2d40.webp?t=1759909615\" width=446 height=26 /></span><br>为了在气候变化后地球的寒冷大气层带来的全球性灾难中生存下来，人类对自己进行了基因改造，使自己具有动物的特征。通过基因剪接获得的毛皮可以帮助人类应对严寒天气，而冬眠的能力则可以让人类在漫长的星际飞行中安然入睡。《胡修狐》的故事就发生在这个毛茸茸的未来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/1a6e68124214c13966d38c34a7dd050b.avif?t=1759909615\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/38abd80ce5d60f4cbdf8d70e3d59e5c6.webp?t=1759909615\" width=446 height=26 /></span><br>上世纪90年代初，我父母把我们的第一台电脑带回家——雅达利8位机的波兰山寨版。通过一本旧手册，我学会了如何用Basic编程。从那时起，我就想毕生从事游戏制作。<br><br>时至2012年，在参观了广岛和平纪念公园并目睹了暴力和仇恨的后果之后，我发誓再也不玩或制作暴力游戏了。取而代之的是，我专注于制作能促进善良和友谊的游戏。<br><br>有了Game Jam的经验和亲朋好友的大力支持，制作这款游戏的梦想终于变成了现实。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/f91e77c5a4d5683040a939619c9bd703.poster.avif?t=1759909615\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/f91e77c5a4d5683040a939619c9bd703.webm?t=1759909615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/f91e77c5a4d5683040a939619c9bd703.mp4?t=1759909615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/387059a89e48307d57c047e0c2dc123f.webp?t=1759909615\" width=446 height=30 /></span><br>《胡修狐》由我——Jaroslav Meloun设计、编写、绘制和编程，我对健康的故事、科幻和冒险游戏充满激情。<br><br>音乐由才华横溢的Aleix Ramon编写和制作。<br><br>薇克丝的主要美术设计由了不起的Jana Kilianová创作。<br><br>我的愿望是，你也能像我一样梦想成真！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696220/extras/19d8bceabbf4c67d1c322f292fdadfab.avif?t=1759909615\" width=601 height=91 /></span> ",
